# Input

```scss
---
title: Title
description: Description
---

a {
  color: red;
}

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,8 +1,3 @@
----
-title: Title
-description: Description
----
-
-a {
+--- title:Title description:Description --- a {
   color: red;
 }
```

# Output

```scss
--- title:Title description:Description --- a {
  color: red;
}
```
